data.description: SPECIAL LOW INTEREST RATE OPPORTUNITY!! Call agent for details!! Limited opportunity!! Capture magnificent sunsets and immerse yourself in the beautiful nature this property has to offer surrounded by lush trees and mountain views. This meticulously maintained and cared for model-like home on .66 acres with its' inviting atmosphere and air of unmistakable quality catches your attention as soon as you walk in.  Double doors open to a charming living room with a wood burning fireplace that is adjacent to an upgraded kitchen.  Two bedrooms and one new remodel bath on the main floor with brand new subway tile shower. Three bedrooms and two baths on the upstairs level with hillside views and beautiful wood ceilings.  Reflecting quality everywhere you turn you see wood shutters, upgraded floors, and new kitchen cabinets and a barn door inviting you into the large second living room, entertainment room, game room or dining room. To top it off there is an expansive multi-level entertaining backyard which truly adds a level of luxury featuring a comfortable gazebo to enjoy the view, a beautiful pool with a deck and 8-person spa to enjoy day and night.   Professional landscaping and sprinkler system help maintain the property. Paid for solar, therefore providing a great saving on utilities.  There is a detached double car garage for storage and work area. Space to build a garden and a surprise adorable custom shed for a workspace, painter's dream house, creative space, so many uses.  With its' beautiful trees and mountain views from almost every window and patio this property provides relaxation and fun. The property has an extended list of upgrades too long to list.  This turn-key home is a must see that will leave you with a lasting impression. Enjoy the benefits of Dixon Lake within one mile that offers recreational boating, fishing and camping, hiking trails and picnic areas.
